# Tailwind UI Patterns

## 概览页结构
```javascript
<div className="h-full flex flex-col bg-gray-50">
    {/* 标题区 */}
    <div className="bg-white border-b px-6 py-4">
        <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div className="w-10 h-10 bg-{color}-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <Icon className="w-5 h-5 text-{color}-600" />
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 className="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">页面标题</h1>
                <p className="text-sm text-gray-500">页面描述</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    {/* 内容区 */}
    <div className="flex-1 p-6">
        {/* 统计卡片 grid */}
        <div className="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-6">
            {/* stat cards */}
        </div>
        
        {/* 主内容 */}
        <div className="bg-white rounded-lg border border-dashed border-gray-300 p-12">
            {/* placeholder or content */}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
```

## 列表页结构
```javascript
<ModuleLayout>
    <div className="space-y-4">
        {/* 筛选栏 */}
        <div className="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center">
                <input className="px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg text-sm" />
                <select className="px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg text-sm"></select>
                <button className="px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-lg text-sm">
                    查询
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        {/* 表格 */}
        <div className="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <table className="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
                {/* table content */}
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</ModuleLayout>
```

## 状态标签
```javascript
<span className="px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-800 rounded text-xs">启用</span>
<span className="px-2 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 rounded text-xs">禁用</span>
<span className="px-2 py-1 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 rounded text-xs">待处理</span>
<span className="px-2 py-1 bg-red-100 text-red-800 rounded text-xs">异常</span>
<span className="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded text-xs">进行中</span>
```

## 按钮样式
```javascript
// 主按钮
<button className="px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded-lg text-sm hover:bg-indigo-700">

// 次按钮
<button className="px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 rounded-lg text-sm hover:bg-gray-50">

// 图标按钮
<button className="p-2 text-gray-500 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
```

## 模块配色参考
- 美国事业部: `bg-rose-500` / `bg-rose-50`
- 中国事业部: `bg-violet-500` / `bg-violet-50`
- 东南亚事业部: `bg-orange-500` / `bg-orange-50`
- 欧洲事业部: `bg-blue-500` / `bg-blue-50`
- 产品中心: `bg-sky-500` / `bg-sky-50`
- 财务中心: `bg-emerald-500` / `bg-emerald-50`
- 质量管理: `bg-cyan-500` / `bg-cyan-50`
